label: Parameters Trx and Charge In Topology
comment: Parameters trx and charge are used in topology

label: Source Availability Activation
comment: 1= Activate Source Availability / 0 = Deactivate Source Availability

label: Compute Mode
comment: 'hourly' to setup aggregation calculation hour by hour, 'daily' to calculate all the hours of a day at the same time

label: Limit hours to switch compute mode
comment: Limit hours to switch compute mode

label: Extrapolation - Number of time agregations
comment: Number of time aggregations on which search extrapolated datas

label: Gis mode
comment: Activation/Deactivation of the GIS module. 0 = GIS module is deactivated ; 1 = 2D and 3D GIS are activated; 2 = 3D GIS only is activated (limited mode for multi SRID countries)

label: Daily statistics history
comment: Number of days of daily statistics are kept in Trending&Aggregation

label: Hourly statistics history
comment: Number of days of hourly statistics are kept in Trending&Aggregation

label: Number maximum of 3rd Axis
comment: Number maximum of 3rd Axis elements uploaded in the Topology

label: Number of Counters/KPIs
comment: Maximum number of active Counters/KPIs allowed

label: Module Name
comment: Name of the module (must be set with lower characters e.g iu,gb)

label: Product Name
comment: Name of the product

label: Product Version
comment: Version of the product

label: Report Files History
comment: Number of days of filed reports are kept in Trending&Aggregation (by default the value is set to 120)

label: Delete data files during retrieve process
comment: 0: delete disabled, 1: delete enabled

label: Search data files into sub-directories
comment: 0: sub-directories disabled, 1: sub-directories enabled

label: Topology file location
comment: Full path to topology file

label: Vendor Name
comment: Vendor Name for the use or Global application

label: 'Critical' Alarm display color
comment: Color used for the display of 'Critical' level alarms (default is set to #f88484)

label: 'Major' Alarm display color
comment: Color used for the display of 'Major' level alarms (default is set to #fab308)

label: Alarm management Refresh
comment: Alarm management automatic refresh periodicity

label: 'Minor' Alarm display color
comment: Color used for the display of 'Minor' level alarms (default is set to #f7fa08)

label: Alarm results limit
comment: Maximum number of results allowed for an alarm (by default it is set to 1000)

label: Alarm Systems Activation
comment: Activate/Deactivate the management alarm systems for files missing (0 = deactivate, 1 = activate)

label: Top/Worst List results
comment: Number of results by Top/Worst List (by default it is set to 10)

label: Duration delay for capture end time
comment: Delay in (s) substracted from capture end time to define data hour

label: Automatic Email Activation
comment: Activate/Deactivate the automatic email sending for alarms, reports (0=deactivate, 1=activate)

label: Autorefresh delay
comment: Delay in minute to refresh dashboards and GIS

label: Backup Database directory
comment: Directory where the database backup is stored

label: Base Component version
comment: Version of the Base Component

label: Capture Duration
comment: Time (sec.) during a capture has be performed by a probe (by default the value is set to 3600)
Maximum number of queries executed to find ne in Overtime

label: Monthly statistics history
comment: Number of months of monthly statistics are kept in Trending&Aggregation

label: Weekly statistics history
comment: Number of weeks of weekly statistics are kept in Trending&Aggregation

label: Investigation dashboard - Number of selection
comment: Number of network elements allowed for selection in the Investigation dashboard (by default it is set to 15)
Label of BTS in exported Google Earth File

label: Link To Activity Analysis
comment: 0 = deactivate, 1 = activate link to Activity Analysis on contextuel menu

label: Database and servers history for Activity Analysis
comment: Number of days of data available in Trending&Aggregation (by default : 60 days)

label: Reply To
comment: Reply email address used in the automatic email sendings

label: number of charts with interactive data
comment: Maximum number of charts displayed in a dashboard that will contain interactive data

label: Numbers maximum results displayed during a topology upload
comment: Numbers maximum results displayed during a topology upload

label: Maximum execution time of a process
comment: Maximum execution time of a process (in minutes)

label: Number of characters displayed for network agregation label in the filter
comment: Number of characters displayed for network agregation label in the filter

label: Number of probes
comment: Number of probes installed that provide data to Trending&Aggregation

label: Reliability Indicator mode
comment: Activation/Deactivation of the Reliability indicator in the graph. 1 = activated 0 = deactivated

label: Axe3 separator
comment: Separator used in axe3

label: SNMP trap activation
comment: 0 = deactivate SNMP traps, 1 = activate SNMP traps

label: SNMP Server Port
comment: Port on which the SNMP Traps will be sent

label: SNMP Server
comment: IP address of the server that will receive the SNMP Traps

label: SNMP trap format version
comment: Version of the format used to send SNMP traps (either 1 for version 1 or 2c)

label: Iurlink statistics flag
comment: 0 = Iurlink stats disable

label: Iublink statistics flag
comment: 0 = Iublink stats disable

label: Adjacencies statistics flag
comment: 0 = Adjacencies stats disable

label: Lac statistics flag
comment: 0 = Lac stats disable

label: Rac statistics flag
comment: 0 = Rac stats disable

label: Node-B statistics flag
comment: 0 = Node-B stats disable

label: RNC statistics flag
comment: 0 = RNC stats disable

comment:
Possible named colors :

 - red
 - green
 - blue

label: Timer Builder Report
comment: Maximum running time allowed for a query from the 'Query Builder' before it is automatically killed (by default it is set to 300 seconds)

label: Automatic topology update
comment: 1=Enable 0=Disable automatic topology update. If set to 1, the parameter 'Topology file location' needs to be filled in

label: Update of x,y or azimuth
comment: 0=>not changes 1=>update of x,y or azimuth

label: User statistics Mode
comment: 0 = display statistics on user connections, 1 = display statistics on number of pages viewed

label: First Day of the week
comment: 1 = Week starts on Monday 0 = Week starts on Sunday

label: ErlangB availability
comment: 0 : ErlangB function not available in KPI builder, 1 : ErlangB function available in KPI builder

label: Extrapolation - Activation
comment: Activate Datas Extrapolation

label: Maximum limit of the number of the different collected hour files
comment: Default value : 20 hours

label: Path to product documentation
comment: Path to product documentation (path and file name), example: /doc/doc.pdf

label: Counter value when not present in PM files
comment: 1= Default value when absent , 0 = NULL when absent

label: Counter value when not non-numeric value in PM files
comment: 1= Default value when non-numeric value , 0 = NULL when non-numeric value

label: switch to mono/multi process mode
comment: 0 = Multi process mode activated, 1 = mono process mode

label: Query Builder CSV export expiry date
comment: Removes Query Builder CSV export older than x days.

label: Minimum free disk space (in %) required for Query Builder
comment: This parameter is used to set the minimum free diskspace (in percent) required to launch a CSV export in Query Builder.

label: Enable Performance log during retreive
comment: 0 = performance log disabled

label: Date of the last automapping
comment: Date format : YYYYMMDD
